@node history
@title "History"


 @{bold "29th of June 1997"}
 
 Initial release ... still hopefully 'First And Last And Always'.

 This transfer animation was assembled some time ago, short time after releasing
 AmiTransWorld(1) on 22nd of April 1997 ... but was never released .. until now!

