@node distribution
@title "Distribution"

 The  'AmiTransWorld2'  transfer  animation  is  Copyright  ©  1997   by   Georg
 Rottlaender.


 'AmiTransWorld2'  may be freely distributed as long as the following conditions
 are fulfilled:

 - all files have to be kept together and

 - no file may be modified (especially the transfer animation itself).

 Including this transfer animation in a commercial or shareware distribution (of
 a WWW browser for example), is prohibited without my written  permission.


@endnode

